{"title_page": "Heosphora rhodochros", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = \n| taxon = Heosphora rhodochros\n| authority = [[Alfred Jefferis Turner|Turner]], 1947\n| synonyms = *''Anerastria rhodochros'' <small>Turner, 1947</small>\n}}\n\n'''''Heosphora rhodochros''''' is a species of [[moth]] in the family [[Pyralidae]]. The species was first described by [[Alfred Jefferis Turner]] in 1947.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bie.ala.org.au/species/urn:lsid:biodiversity.org.au:afd.taxon:7bbe3bad-687e-4b96-b2b8-07f0e9998930|title=Species: Heosphora rhodochros|last=Australia|first=Atlas of Living|website=bie.ala.org.au|language=en-AU|access-date=2020-04-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nhm.ac.uk/our-science/data/lepindex/detail/?taxonno=8988&page_no=1&page_size=30|title=LepIndex - rhodochros|website=www.nhm.ac.uk|access-date=2020-04-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.biolib.cz/en/taxon/id1101618/|title=BioLib: Biological library|last=ondrej.zicha(at)gmail.com|first=Ondrej Zicha;|website=www.biolib.cz|access-date=2020-04-20}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n[[Category:Pyralidae]]\n\n\n{{Pyralidae-stub}}\n[[Category:Moths of Australia]]\n[[Category:Taxa described by Alfred Jefferis Turner]]\n[[Category:Moths described in 1947]]\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n| image = \n| taxon = Heosphora rhodochros\n| authority = [[Alfred Jefferis Turner|Turner]], 1947\n| synonyms = *''Anerastria rhodochros'' <small>Turner, 1947</small>\n}}\n\n'''''Heosphora colobela''''' is a species of [[moth]] in the family [[Pyralidae]]. The species was first described by [[Alfred Jefferis Turner]] in 1947.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bie.ala.org.au/species/urn:lsid:biodiversity.org.au:afd.taxon:7bbe3bad-687e-4b96-b2b8-07f0e9998930|title=Species: Heosphora rhodochros|last=Australia|first=Atlas of Living|website=bie.ala.org.au|language=en-AU|access-date=2020-04-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nhm.ac.uk/our-science/data/lepindex/detail/?taxonno=8988&page_no=1&page_size